<title>lḥẓẗ ạlạlạm ạlsẖdydẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- lḥẓẗ ạlạlạm ạlsẖdydẗ ạlly sẖʿrt byhạ wạnạ kẖạṭy

[V2]
 kẖlythạ bdạyẗ sʿydẗ ywm mạ ạʿlnt lk ạnksạry

[V3]
 ywm mạ sẖft ạlạmy ạlly kạnt jwạyạ wsẖft ḍyq ạyạmy mn ḥml ạlkẖṭạyạ

[V4]
 sẖạl ṣlybk tʿby wkl ḍyq jwạyạ

[V5]
 ạlqrạr - ywmhạ ạʿlnt ḍʿfy wqwlt lyk tʿbạn

[V6]
 ywmhạ qwltly ạbny wrjʿt wạnạ frḥạn

[V7]
 2- ʿny ạnt sẖlt ạlḍyqẗ ạlly sbbhạ ạlqlb ạlqạsy

[V8]
 mkạny ʿsẖt ạ̉wqạt mryrẗ ʿlsẖạn tsẖwf ạlkẖyr ạyạmy

[V9]
 ywm mạ ḥmlt ṣlyby wkẖdt ạnt ạlạdạnẗ ạnt qwlt ḥbyby lly ʿạsẖ bqsạwẗ

[V10]
 ạnt sẖgẖlk hmy ḥbytny bkl ạmạnẗ

[V11]
 3- ʿsẖt ạnt whbtny nfsk wạnạ ạstktrt nfsy ʿlyk

[V12]
 wḥyạty ạdythạly bdmk ạnạ ạlly ạẓhrt krhy lyk

[V13]
 ywm mạ sẖftny ʿạjz ʿn ạny ạsẖwf ạlnwr dh sẖry kạn ḥạjz ʿny ạy srwr

[V14]
 kạnt lḥẓẗ mylạdy ywm rfʿ ạlmṣlwb</lyrics>
</song>